12::[Ignitions]::
2Ignitions are special and more powerful boosts that you may purchase in the shop. Unlike weapon boosts, these boosts do not require TP to consume.  Instead they require some of your Ignition Gauge. Each Ignition requires a certain # of your Ignition Gauge to activate and then a certain amount per turn to keep active.
12::[How do I use an ignition?]::
2IN BATTLE, after purchasing one, you may use the command /me goes <ignition name>